Subject: Lost Reverse

Hello everyone,

I just took my 78 Westy out for her first run around
the block.  Aside from running out of gas everything
ran well.  However, after gassing up and returning
home, I went to place it in reverse and nothing.  It
will shift into position but when I let the clutch out
nothing.  All other gears engage okay.  I did try
