reverse once but then lost it so I know its most
likely a question of proper adjustment.  I'm thinking
there is a better way than messing with the plate and
any advise is appreciated.

Also, noticed speedo was not working.  I pulled front
left hub and pulled cable out, it was about 18" long. 
How long should it be?

Thanks again,
